rvice 的响应也显著恶化。\n   - Trace 数据并未直接显示 Node 资源使用问题，但需与 Metric 数据证据对齐，以共同验证。\n\n### 结合综合假设验证工作\nAdService 自身以及它所在 Node 的资源压力是主要调查目标。下一步需要进行更多验证以达成根因共识，现有进展为：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"latency_spike\",\n    \"frontend->adservice\",\n    \"context_deadline_exceeded\",\n    \"redis_hget_delay\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Frontend 在调用 AdService 的过程中频繁超时 (context deadline exceeded)，且延迟的倍数超过可接受范围。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Trace 数据表明异常耗时升高至正常值的 2.27 倍，同时错误状态明确指出 `context deadline exceeded`。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"node aiops-k8s-04\",\n      \"reason\": \"多个服务发生性能问题集中在该节点，包括 CurrencyService (延迟 5 倍) 和 AdService。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"AdService pod 与 CurrencyService pod 同时驻留于此，延迟和故障行为可能由于节点资源问题传播。\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "report_analysis_findings": {"uuid": "1ef94bd7-352", "component": "adservice-0", "reason": "error_ratio on adservice-0 increased, causing latency spike and context deadline exceeded.", "reasoning_trace": [{"step": 1, "action": "LoadMetrics(adservice)", "observation": "error_ratio on adservice-0 rose to 0.81, increasing latency spike."}, {"step": 2, "action": "LogSearch(frontend)", "observation": "Error logs showing 'context deadline exceeded' with rpc error."}, {"step": 3, "action": "TraceAnalysis(1ef94bd7-352)", "observation": "Frontend->AdService shows latency spike, context deadline exceeded."}]}, "report_analysis_completed": true}
